metadata.name: Alpha Codes #1
metadata.description: Alpha Codes is a gateway to an exclusive, strategically planned movement that already has and will continue to attract top performers across the world. Alpha Codes is aimed at providing holders unique value and encouragement to share your story, perspective, and voice in a number of community led initiatives. Our holders will be provided with the opportunity to participate in an ecosystem of rewards for partaking in our initiatives that are carefully crafted for creating a better you.
